        {
          "cells": [
            {
              "raw_text": "2.2.4 操作方法2.2.4.1取本品，除去薄膜衣，研细，取细粉        (约相当于泮托拉唑10mg)，加水       ml（20ml），振摇使泮托拉唑钠溶解，滤过，取滤液       ml（2ml），加稀盐酸       滴（5滴），滴加硅钨酸试液，即产生                。2.2.4.2取含量测定项下的溶液，照分光光度法（通则0401）在        nm（292nm±2nm）的波长处有最大吸收，在        nm（250nm±2nm）的波长处有最小吸收。2.2.5 标准规定内控标准：①应产生白色絮状沉淀；②取含量测定项下的溶液，照分光光度法(通则0401)在292nm±2nm的波长处有最大吸收，在250nm±2nm的波长处有最小吸收。 2.2.6 实验结果异常处理                                                  □是       □否  实验室异常情况编号_______________________________________________2.2.7 清场将检验用具及废弃物分类。                                           □是        □否关闭电源。                                                         □是        □否",
              "parts": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "2.2.4 操作方法2.2.4.1取本品，除去薄膜衣，研细，取细粉"
                },
                {
                  "type": "line",
                  "field_key": "layout/pantoprazole/finished/identification/t0_r14_c0_p0_line",
                  "width": "56px"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "(约相当于泮托拉唑10mg)，加水"
                },
                {
                  "type": "line",
                  "field_key": "layout/pantoprazole/finished/identification/t0_r14_c0_p1_line",
                  "width": "49px"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "ml（20ml），振摇使泮托拉唑钠溶解，滤过，取滤液"
                },
                {
                  "type": "line",
                  "field_key": "layout/pantoprazole/finished/identification/t0_r14_c0_p2_line",
                  "width": "49px"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "ml（2ml），加稀盐酸"
                },
                {
                  "type": "line",
                  "field_key": "layout/pantoprazole/finished/identification/t0_r14_c0_p3_line",
                  "width": "49px"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "滴（5滴），滴加硅钨酸试液，即产生"
                },
                {
                  "type": "line",
                  "field_key": "layout/pantoprazole/finished/identification/t0_r14_c0_p4_line",
                  "width": "112px"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "。2.2.4.2取含量测定项下的溶液，照分光光度法（通则0401）在"
                },
                {
                  "type": "line",
                  "field_key": "layout/pantoprazole/finished/identification/t0_r14_c0_p5_line",
                  "width": "56px"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "nm"
                },
                {
                  "type": "note",
                  "text": "（292nm±2nm）"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "的波长处有最大吸收，在"
                },
                {
                  "type": "line",
                  "field_key": "layout/pantoprazole/finished/identification/t0_r14_c0_p7_line",
                  "width": "56px"
                },
